fields.title: Figth of the titans
fields.text: Two strongest men - Jakub Nitkiewicz and Mariusz Pudzianowski - had finally an oportunity to participate in an event together. They were lifting for days. Many world records were beaten during those weeks. Unfortunately for Mariusz, he lost, 31:1. The only one competition he won was shopping bags lifting. He won because his oponennt was disqualified because he was eating from his shopping bags during competition.
